## Decisions and Action Items

* **Decisions**:
  * The WGLC for the HPKE with JWE draft will be declared closed, and the document will return to the IESG.
  * The WGLC for [draft-ietf-jose-deprecate-none-rsa15](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-jose-deprecate-none-rsa15/) will be declared closed based on in-room consensus, and the document will proceed to publication.
  * The JOSE-specific portions of [draft-ietf-jose-pqc-kem](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-jose-pqc-kem/) will be removed, and the draft will be fully transferred to the COSE working group.

* **Action Items**:
  * **Chairs**: Issue a formal working group call for adoption for Christian Paquin's draft, *BBS and Modular Sub-proofs with JSON Web Proofs*.
  * **Chairs / AD**: Coordinate with CFRG leadership and authors to expedite the progress of the BBS signature specifications.
  * **Lucas (Draft Author)**: Initiate a dedicated thread on the mailing list to resolve the ECDSA component encoding (raw vs. ASN.1 DER) for [draft-ietf-jose-pq-composite-sigs](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-jose-pq-composite-sigs/).

